<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Loan Approved</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #f0fff4;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .success-container {
            z-index: 10;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #1a7732;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .home-btn {
            margin-top: 25px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: none;
            background-color: #1a7732;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .home-btn:hover {
            background-color: #145a26;
        }

        canvas {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 9999;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-container">
        <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Hurray!! ðŸŽ‰</br> Your Loan Has Been Approved</h1>
        <p>Enjoy your funds and don't forget to repay on time to maintain a good credit score.</p>
        <button class="home-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/'">Back</button>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/canvas-confetti@1.6.0/dist/confetti.browser.min.js">
